TY  - JOUR
TI  - Personal Attributes, Job Performance, and Probability of Promotion
AU  - Wise, David A.
AB  - [The empirical content of the paper is the relationship between personal attributes and job performance, as measured by rate of promotion, in a large corporation. It focuses, however, on a behavioral model and method of estimation which provide a natural way of dealing with this and similar phenomena.]
